data.description: Welcome to this charming home nestled in a great Seabrook location on a quiet cul-de-sac. This updated 2 story home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths with heigh ceilings. During the cold nights, enjoy the warm fireplace. Hardwood flooring and tile throughout the home with no carpet. This Seabrook gem has a great backyard.
